      "role": "user",
      "content": "so if there's no physical signal or medium between them, how does the second particle even \"know\" what the first one did? it feels like there's some kind of hidden mechanism or trick going on behind the scenes that we just can't see. is there any official theory on what might be happening in that gap?",
